WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.166 --> 00:00:03.966
I scared your hand when you just played Qixi Festival

2
00:00:04.200 --> 00:00:06.566
Are you having a holiday with him?

3
00:00:06.566 --> 00:00:08.433
He is a daughter

4
00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:10.100
He drugged me.

5
00:00:10.100 --> 00:00:12.700
You deserve to beat me and frame me

6
00:00:12.700 --> 00:00:14.400
I'm just a scary person

7
00:00:14.900 --> 00:00:16.200
How could I hold a grudge against him?

8
00:00:16.200 --> 00:00:17.066
That's not what I meant.

9
00:00:17.066 --> 00:00:19.933
I'm doing this to him today because I don't like him

10
00:00:19.933 --> 00:00:21.233
A nice girl

11
00:00:21.666 --> 00:00:23.366
Disregarding the pain of loved ones

12
00:00:23.366 --> 00:00:25.900
Hurt yourself for a scum

13
00:00:26.300 --> 00:00:27.700
If you think I'm doing something wrong

14
00:00:27.700 --> 00:00:28.966
Can I go?

15
00:00:30.566 --> 00:00:31.566
Don't go

16
00:00:33.100 --> 00:00:35.600
You don't even know who I am, why did you keep me?

17
00:00:36.466 --> 00:00:37.500
Long Chenguang

18
00:00:38.466 --> 00:00:39.600
You shouldn't have told me

19
00:00:40.333 --> 00:00:41.500
So many years

20
00:00:41.533 --> 00:00:43.066
I've been waiting for someone

21
00:00:43.300 --> 00:00:44.966
Waiting for a chance to repay

22
00:00:45.333 --> 00:00:48.166
But I can't find him, you let me go

23
00:00:49.133 --> 00:00:50.166
Ye Chenguang

24
00:00:51.533 --> 00:00:53.066
You showed up

25
00:00:53.400 --> 00:00:55.666
In the end it was fate

26
00:00:56.200 --> 00:00:57.566
Relive

27
00:00:57.733 --> 00:01:00.166
Can I also enjoy it a little bit?

28
00:01:00.166 --> 00:01:02.000
The youth I missed in my previous life

